name: __EPingType
doc: Flags specifying different types of ping.

RoundTripExclFrame: Round Trip ping which includes any server/client frame time delay
ICMP: Round Trip ping which may attempt to exclude server frame time delay (inaccurate)
UDPQoS: Standard ICMP ping (GameNetDriver client only, accuracy affected by network ICMP throttling)
Max: Standard ICMP ping (GameNetDriver client only, accuracy affected by network ICMP throttling)
Count: Round Trip ping which may attempt to exclude server frame time delay (inaccurate)
